<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    {{ title|raw }}
    {{ meta_description|raw }}

    <!-- OGP Tags -->
    {{ og_title|raw }}
    {{ og_description|raw }}
    {{ og_image|raw }}
    {{ og_url|raw }}
    {{ og_type|raw }}

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">

    {% block head %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
    <header class="site-header">
        <div class="header-container">
            <a href="/" class="site-logo">
                <img src="/img/site-logo.webp" alt="Nave-wata Logo" />
                <span class="site-title">Nave-wata</span>
            </a>
            <nav class="site-navigation">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">ホーム</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">お問い合わせ</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container main-content">
        {% block content %}{% endblock %}
    </div>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="footer-container">
            <div class="footer-section">
                <a href="/" class="footer-author">
                    <img src="/img/author/nave-wata.webp" alt="著者プロフィール" width="50" height="50"/>
                    <h3>Nave-wata</h3>
                </a>
                <p>エンジニアリングの知識や備忘録などを気が向けば投稿します</p>
                <p>投稿内容を元になにか問題や不具合など発生してしまっても、<br class="min-md-br"/>何ら責任を負えませんのであしからず...</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-section">
                <h3>リンク</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">お問い合わせ</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/privacy-policy">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Nave-wata. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
